  <h1>Pricing</h1>
  <div id="pricing" class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-4 wow bounceInDown" data-wow-delay="0.2s">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2>Pricing.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="lead">
        Cookies start at $2 each. For a larger and more complex cookie, there will be an additional charge. Message us and let us know what you're looking for and we can help give you ideas for your theme and can give you a better idea on what the pricing will be!
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-4 wow bounceInDown" data-wow-delay="0.5s">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2>Notice.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="lead">
        The more notice, the better! It takes us days to mix, cut and bake, make frosting, decorate, and package. We require at least a minimum of 7 days   notice. If you do have a last minute rush order, feel free to contact us and we can always see if we can make it work! We do, however, charge an additional fee for rush orders.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-4 wow bounceInDown" data-wow-delay="0.8s">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2>Shipping.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="lead">
        Yes. We do ship! It stresses us out, but we'll do it! Just for you! We package our cookies as carefully as we can and pray they make it to you in one piece. All orders go out priority 2-day to ensure freshness! S & H fees depend on how many cookies you order and typically start at about $15 for about 2-3 dozen. 
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
